title: info

`----` and longer rules become `---`, even in fidelity mode.

Why: the parse tree records a bare `hr` element without the dash count,
and the serializer emits three dashes by choice.

* Covers: $:/plugins/tiddlywiki/wikitext-serialize/rules/horizrule.js.
* Mode: fidelity (no mode field: this pair pins a normalization that happens even with the source available).
